    and Welwyn Garden City. See also Table 2, note (c).

    Welwyn Garden City. See also Table 2, note (g).
Renamed 23.2.1982 to become the parish of Northaw & Cuffley.

    Table 2, note (g).

Created 1.10.1921 from the parishes of Hatfield, Digswell, Tewin and Welwyn. Abolished 1.4.1974 to become the Welwyn Hatfield unparished area. 
    See also Table 2, notes (b) and (e).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish of Welwyn 
    Garden City. See also Table 2, note (g).

Created 1.4.2000 out of the parish of Welwyn. See also Table 
    2, note (g).
